data.title: The Action for Learning Partnership, Bedford Education Action Zone Order 1999
data.meta_description: This Order establishes the Action for Learning Partnership, Bedford Education Action Zone, which comprises the schools listed in Schedule 2. The Order also provides (in articles 4 and 5) for the membership of the Education Action Forum for the zone.
